```
(32, 32, 3) (32, 32, 3) OK
(32, 32, 3) (32, 32, 3) OK
(32, 32, 3) (32, 32, 3) OK
(32, 32, 3) (32, 32, 3) OK
(32, 32, 3) (32, 32, 3) OK
