864,IssueCommentEvent,2015-06-25 01:01:21+00:00,7568434,paulfitz/daff,79913,tsibley,,,90144626,115058822,"Vanilla git-diff still includes the `---` and `+++` lines after the rename block (`git_args[8]`), so maybe daff should too?  The `+++ b/` line in that case should use `git_args[7]` instead of `path`.  (I'd offer a patch myself, but I'm not setup to hack on daff at the moment due to haxe version issues.)

