1534,IssueCommentEvent,2017-03-05 03:14:39+00:00,1206729,hhatto/autopep8,1337598,evhub,,,201191916,284201955,"@hhatto `except:` and `except Exception:` are not equivalent, and having `autopep8` change one into to other has the potential to cause some serious issues, like raising errors that should be caught. I just ran into some such errors caused by this change myself. I would suggest changing `except:` into `except BaseException:` instead, since those are in fact equivalent.",{},,User,False
