2772,IssueCommentEvent,2015-04-15 17:04:05+00:00,1938370,Mottie/tablesorter,136959,Mottie,,,68719362,93487745,"Hi @lbstoller!

The math widget does not target the `thead` when calculating or displaying results. Although, you could use the [`match_complete` callback](http://mottie.github.io/tablesorter/docs/example-widget-math.html#math_complete) to target any HTML in the `thead`.

```js
// complete executed after each function
math_complete : function($cell, wo, result, value, arry){
    $cell.closest('table').find('thead .totals').html( result );
    return result;
}
```
",{},,User,False
