2833,IssueCommentEvent,2015-05-15 16:37:13+00:00,5879214,berkerpeksag/astor,2379062,pmaupin,,,76603659,102454878,"As one who previously did a lot of cleanup on this module, I would like to propose a small change.  Sorry about not making a patch, but I don't have a current checkout handy and my git-fu is not up to snuff...

The new patch has several functions changed to look something like this:

```python
def visit_FunctionDef(self, node, async=False):
        self.decorators(node, 1)
        self.statement(node, '%sdef %s(' %
                        ('async ' if async else '', node.name))
        ...
```
I personally think it would be clearer (and faster) (and a smaller diff from the original) like this:
```python
def visit_FunctionDef(self, node, defstmt='def'):
        self.decorators(node, 1)
        self.statement(node, '%s %s(' % (defstmt, node.name))
        ...
```

Thank you and best regards,
Pat
",{},,User,False
