3099,IssueCommentEvent,2017-10-16 04:36:10+00:00,1510462,stefankoegl/kdtree,480406,grapemix,,,265644363,336778341,"The search_nn_dist() return unexpected result to me too and the test case for search_nn_dist() also miss some points. For example, in the test case:

points = [(x,y) for x in range(10) for y in range(10)]
tree = kdtree.create(points)
nn = tree.search_nn_dist((5,5), 2.5)

