I don't think this is a hard problem to solve, I believe I just need to write up a custom decoder that I use when I load the JSON in. I'll get to it as soon as I can, but in the meantime, maybe you should try YAML. I tend to prefer it. Personally, I think it's easier to read than JSON and I love the fact that I can comment all of my fixtures. ",{},,User,False
