5695,IssueCommentEvent,2015-04-18 08:37:42+00:00,12420595,CamDavidsonPilon/lifelines,223655,spacecowboy,,,69246780,94144453,"This is excellent. I had actually never heard of an O(nlogn) implementation before. Doing some ""expert googling"" turns up a single reference in the literature:

