6890,IssueCommentEvent,2017-05-11 22:35:25+00:00,24774658,boto/boto3,2643092,JordonPhillips,327752,boto,227862409,300935344,"The CLI automatically paginates for you, boto3 does not. You'll need to paginate to get all the results. For example:

```python
import boto3


iam = boto3.client('iam')
paginator = iam.get_paginator('list_policies')

for page in pagniator.paginate(Scope='All'):
    # do something fun
```",{},,User,False
