6900,IssueCommentEvent,2015-08-13 20:09:03+00:00,6670942,boto/botocore,90788,mjschultz,327752,boto,97972490,130824927,"I have a [PR](https://github.com/boto/botocore/pull/627) that adds paginators for *most* of those except `get_log_events`.

`get_log_events` is a bit weird because it returns both a `nextForwardToken` and a `nextBackwardToken` and the one you'd want to use depends on if you set `startFromHead` or not. The token itself is also different from other APIs in that the `next*Token` will be a repeat on the last page (and the `events` list will be empty). So I'm not sure of the best way to handle that.

All that said, I'd rather have the other paginations in with that one missing then follow up with the `get_log_events` down the road.",{},,User,False
