7118,IssueCommentEvent,2015-03-14 06:09:53+00:00,2866041,kivy/python-for-android,769155,jasonxunxu,1266152,kivy,61445195,79973814,"It turns out that the `twisted` recipe (and maybe some other recipes) changed `PYTHONPATH`:
```bash
export PYTHONPATH=$SITEPACKAGES_PATH:$BUILDLIB_PATH
```
which was then mistakenly picked up by venv, leading to the missing `setuptools`.

