7981,IssueCommentEvent,2018-06-15 19:12:27+00:00,6235174,conda/conda,1086317,hanslovsky,6392739,conda,222551876,397716560,"Would it be possible to install an optional dependency by default but not fail if the user chooses not to install that dependency (which would reqiured an additional switch). That would be desirable in my use case, something like this (very simplified):
```
