package A with jdk depends on jdk
package A without jdk does not depend on jdk
```
instead I would like to have something like
```
jdk
package A optional dependence on jdk (but installs jdk by default)
```

This could probably also be achieved in a similar way by what @kalefranz suggests, so I am curious to learn what the timeline would be for that:
