8521,IssueCommentEvent,2018-06-26 17:11:26+00:00,79584587,yahoo/TensorFlowOnSpark,3676078,leewyang,16574,yahoo,333826885,400392772,"@mohammedayub44 that log shows the following: `PermissionDeniedError: hdfs://10.10.10.100:8020/user/mayub/mnist/mnist_model2; Permission denied`

Note: the 'NoneType' error is typically a symptom of an upstream error, not a root cause.  To help identify the root cause, you can try adding `--conf spark.task.maxFailures=1` to your spark-submit command line.  

