8603,IssueCommentEvent,2016-09-02 19:17:46+00:00,43852872,PulpQE/pulp-smash,48132,elyezer,14839747,PulpQE,174825659,244464548,"What about explaining what should be the expected behavior on each TestCase class docstring? For example when using `require_signature` == False and `allowed_keys` == [valid_key] then pulp should only sync signed contents using the valid key and unsigned content, any content signed with a different key will be skipped.

