8726,IssueCommentEvent,2018-02-02 00:03:25+00:00,34864402,apache/incubator-mxnet,18629099,marcoabreu,47359,apache,293394554,362442823,"Since Chris already responded, I'll skip answering above questions. If you would like me to elaborate anyways, feel free to give me a heads up @mli .

