9722,IssueCommentEvent,2018-02-28 03:28:24+00:00,38581626,pybind/pybind11,4459524,jagerman,17565521,pybind,300059407,369109572,"If `A` objects are never used independently in Python, you can bind them with:
```
py::class_<MyClass, std::unique_ptr<MyClass, py::nodelete>>(...)
