9731,IssueCommentEvent,2017-11-16 19:39:41+00:00,38581626,pybind/pybind11,5289944,eirrgang,17565521,pybind,274614802,345039397,"Yes, it is from specifying a base class that isn't pybind-registered, but with the function argument version py::class_<Class>(m, ""Class"", base)
