 I would check Nginx configuration file of one of the working domains, and compare it against iuni.se nginx configuration. You should find a location block something along the line of this:
```
    location ^~ /.well-known/acme-challenge/ {
      default_type ""text/plain"";
      root /usr/local/ispconfig/interface/acme;
    }
```",{},MEMBER,User,False
