10723,IssueCommentEvent,2015-08-07 18:41:22+00:00,14993021,ipython/traitlets,4041990,rmorshea,230453,ipython,98932255,128791777,"So having dug deeper into the issue I was encountering with matplotlib I think I need more than just silent setting. Essentially it the problem is that I'm trying to emulate a getters/setters with traitlets, and the fact that with getters/setters you still have access to the ""private"" value that's hidden behind them. It means that with setters/getters you can do four things:

