11988,IssueCommentEvent,2017-01-06 03:59:51+00:00,22601443,OpenKMIP/PyKMIP,8269688,PeterHamilton,8350747,OpenKMIP,189811052,270826116,"Looking again at the server log you posted, there are a bunch of SQLAlchemy errors when looking up secrets. I haven't been able to reproduce those errors in my test runs (the only error I had was operation failure for `GetAttributeList` since it wasn't supported). In theory those errors shouldn't be occurring; the test suite usually creates the secrets it then tries to retrieve. This looks like it's just failing to create the secrets.

I'll keep an eye out for these errors you were getting as I keep working on the test suite. If you still see these whenever you run the integration tests again let me know.",{},,User,False
