13232,IssueCommentEvent,2018-05-28 04:13:09+00:00,15510254,openfisca/openfisca-core,222463,MattiSG,1794404,openfisca,315760941,392414231,"> calling a method from another method

These are actually not methods but formulas of variables. There is no support for factoring code this way in OpenFisca, because variables model legislation, and legislation does not factor its computation formulas: it either duplicates formulas or reuses the result of another one. Variables align with this behaviour.

> The documentation was then quite easy to follow for our use case.

🎉 https://github.com/openfisca/openfisca-doc/pull/134 proven right",{},MEMBER,User,False
