    ""mimeType"": ""multipart/form-data"",
    ""params"": [],
    ""text"" : ""plain posted data"",
    ""comment"": """"
}
mimeType [string] - Mime type of posted data.
params [array] - List of posted parameters (in case of URL encoded parameters).
text [string] - Plain text posted data
