15426,IssueCommentEvent,2016-10-04 20:20:40+00:00,2747590,lincolnloop/python-qrcode,18078417,TheWingineer,1964,lincolnloop,180972851,251501188,"I'm using version 5.3 with Python 2.7.6. When I use the command line implementation to write out a PNG, the QR code looks normal. An example bad string is ""This is just a test.""

