16009,IssueCommentEvent,2017-10-16 22:15:51+00:00,12407457,Exa-Networks/exabgp,30638845,nfz1,5339170,Exa-Networks,251784687,337059762,"Here is a stack trace from the above error, hopefully this will help:

```
Traceback (most recent call last):
  File ""/usr/local/lib/python3.5/dist-packages/exabgp/reactor/async.py"", line 52, in run
    six.next(generator)
  File ""/usr/local/lib/python3.5/dist-packages/exabgp/reactor/api/command/announce.py"", line 406, in callback
    reactor.configuration.inject_refresh(peers,refresh)
  File ""/usr/local/lib/python3.5/dist-packages/exabgp/configuration/configuration.py"", line 103, in inject_refresh
    family = (refresh.afi,refresh.safi)
AttributeError: 'list' object has no attribute 'afi'
```

I implemented a quick fix for the error. It may not be a good idea to actually implement the fix this way but I just wanted to see if the route-refresh messages are being received okay.

```
index 95a39a8..db4e603 100644
--- a/lib/exabgp/reactor/api/command/announce.py
+++ b/lib/exabgp/reactor/api/command/announce.py
@@ -403,6 +403,9 @@ def announce_refresh (self, reactor, service, command):
                        yield True
                        return
 
+               if isinstance(refresh, list):
+                       refresh = refresh[0]
                reactor.configuration.inject_refresh(peers,refresh)
                self.log_message(""Sent to %s : %s"" % (', '.join(peers if peers else []) if peers is not None else 'all peers',refresh.extensive()))
```

The patch you provided seems to fix the route-refresh received message problem. I also noticed another issue. The JSON string for the route-refresh message is invalid. The route-refresh section has strings that are not double quoted.

```
{  
   ""exabgp"":""4.0.1"",
   ""time"":1508190815.0027232,
   ""host"":""amp-server"",
   ""pid"":22799,
   ""ppid"":21514,
   ""counter"":5,
   ""type"":""refresh"",
   ""neighbor"":{  
      ""address"":{  
         ""local"":""10.0.2.1"",
         ""peer"":""10.0.2.2""
      },
      ""asn"":{  
         ""local"":1,
         ""peer"":2
      },
      ""direction"":""receive"",
      ""route-refresh"":{  
         ""subtype"":query,
         ""safi"":unicast,
         ""afi"":ipv4
      }
   }
}
```",{},NONE,User,False
