If you use wrong credentials and check ""remember me"" you'll always get ""check the log"" and don't get the chance to enter correct credentials.

Just two additional thoughts:

* for ""Send email"" you may want to add the application name as prefix for the ticket, leading to [HackEdit][Enhancement] / [OpenCobolIDE][Bug]
* the shortcuts in this dialogue are a little be strange (did not checked before): Report a bug is ""t"" (I'd have expected ""b""), Suggest an enhancement is ""g"" (expected ""e""), the others don't have shortcuts (would expect title->t, description->d, github->g, email->e or m)",{},,User,False
