17555,IssueCommentEvent,2018-04-29 22:53:28+00:00,43023379,hackingmaterials/atomate,577107,shyuep,14116185,hackingmaterials,152894477,385288318,"I don't think (iv) will change probability of convergence much. This is after in the static calculation, where you are already started from a well-relaxed geometry as well as CHGCAR.

